<h1>1. FUNDAMENTOS</h1>

<h3 id="1.1">1.1 Escolhendo uma Linguagem de Programa√ß√£o</h3>
<p>PHP √© uma linguagem feita para a web. Com ela, voc√™ gera HTML din√¢mico no servidor. √â simples, tem enorme comunidade e √© a base de sistemas como WordPress, Laravel, Facebook (originalmente). Para iniciantes, √© uma escolha certeira porque o retorno √© r√°pido: voc√™ escreve c√≥digo e v√™ o resultado no navegador imediatamente. Al√©m disso, o mercado para PHP continua forte, especialmente em empresas que usam WordPress, Magento, Symfony ou Laravel.</p>

<h3 id="1.2">1.2 Ferramentas do Of√≠cio</h3>
<p>Para come√ßar, voc√™ precisa de um editor de c√≥digo (VS Code, PHPStorm, Sublime), PHP (vers√£o 8.0 ou superior) e um servidor web. Recomendo usar o servidor embutido do PHP para desenvolvimento:</p>
<pre><code><span class="comment"># No terminal, dentro da pasta do projeto:</span>
php -S localhost:8888</code></pre>
<p>Depois, acesse <code>http://localhost:8888</code> no navegador. Outra op√ß√£o √© instalar XAMPP ou Laragon, que j√° incluem Apache, MySQL e PHP.</p>

<h3 id="1.3">1.3 Seu Primeiro C√≥digo PHP</h3>
<p>Crie um arquivo <code>index.php</code> com o conte√∫do:</p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="comment">// Isso √© um coment√°rio em PHP</span>
    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">"Ol√°, mundo!"</span>;
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>
<p><strong>Explica√ß√£o linha a linha:</strong><br>
- <code>&lt;?php</code> abre o bloco de c√≥digo PHP.<br>
- <code>//</code> inicia um coment√°rio de linha √∫nica.<br>
- <code>echo</code> √© um comando que imprime texto na tela.<br>
- <code>?&gt;</code> fecha o bloco PHP (pode ser omitido se o arquivo terminar com PHP).</p>

<h3 id="1.4">1.4 Vari√°veis</h3>
<p>Vari√°veis s√£o "caixinhas" que guardam informa√ß√µes. Em PHP, toda vari√°vel come√ßa com <code>$</code>. Voc√™ pode armazenar textos (strings), n√∫meros, booleanos, etc.</p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="variable">$nome</span> = <span class="string">"Jo√£o"</span>;        <span class="comment">// string</span>
    <span class="variable">$idade</span> = 25;           <span class="comment">// inteiro</span>
    <span class="variable">$altura</span> = 1.75;        <span class="comment">// float</span>
    <span class="variable">$eh_estudante</span> = true;  <span class="comment">// boolean</span>

    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">"Ol√°, $nome! Voc√™ tem $idade anos."</span>;
    <span class="comment">// Concatena√ß√£o com .</span>
    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="string">'Ol√°, ' . $nome . '!'</span>;
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>
<p>As aspas duplas interpretam vari√°veis dentro da string; aspas simples n√£o.</p>

<h3 id="1.5">1.5 Condicionais e Booleanos</h3>
<p>Condicionais (<code>if</code>, <code>else</code>) permitem que o programa tome decis√µes com base em express√µes booleanas.</p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="variable">$livro</span> = <span class="string">"O Pequeno Pr√≠ncipe"</span>;
    <span class="variable">$foi_lido</span> = true;
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span>

&lt;h1&gt;Livro: &lt;?= <span class="variable">$livro</span> ?&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
    &lt;?php <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable">$foi_lido</span>) : ?&gt;
        Voc√™ j√° leu este livro.
    &lt;?php <span class="keyword">else</span> : ?&gt;
        Voc√™ ainda n√£o leu este livro.
    &lt;?php <span class="keyword">endif</span>; ?&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</code></pre>
<p><code>&lt;?= ?&gt;</code> √© atalho para <code>&lt;?php echo ... ?&gt;</code>.</p>

<h3 id="1.6">1.6 Arrays Indexados</h3>
<p>Array √© uma cole√ß√£o de valores. O array indexado usa n√∫meros como posi√ß√£o (come√ßando do 0).</p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="variable">$frutas</span> = [<span class="string">"Ma√ß√£"</span>, <span class="string">"Banana"</span>, <span class="string">"Laranja"</span>];
    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$frutas</span>[0]; <span class="comment">// Ma√ß√£</span>

    <span class="comment">// Percorrendo com foreach</span>
    &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;?php <span class="keyword">foreach</span> (<span class="variable">$frutas</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="variable">$fruta</span>) : ?&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;?= <span class="variable">$fruta</span> ?&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;?php <span class="keyword">endforeach</span>; ?&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>

<h3 id="1.7">1.7 Arrays Associativos</h3>
<p>Array associativo usa chaves nomeadas em vez de n√∫meros. √â como um dicion√°rio.</p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="variable">$livro</span> = [
        <span class="string">'titulo'</span> => <span class="string">'1984'</span>,
        <span class="string">'autor'</span>  => <span class="string">'George Orwell'</span>,
        <span class="string">'ano'</span>    => 1949
    ];

    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$livro</span>[<span class="string">'titulo'</span>]; <span class="comment">// 1984</span>

    <span class="comment">// Itera√ß√£o com chave e valor</span>
    &lt;?php <span class="keyword">foreach</span> (<span class="variable">$livro</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="variable">$chave</span> => <span class="variable">$valor</span>) : ?&gt;
        &lt;p&gt;&lt;?= <span class="variable">$chave</span> ?&gt;: &lt;?= <span class="variable">$valor</span> ?&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;?php <span class="keyword">endforeach</span>; ?&gt;
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>
<p><strong>Operador <code>=></code></strong>: associa uma chave a um valor dentro do array.</p>

<h3 id="1.8">1.8 Fun√ß√µes e Filtros</h3>
<p>Fun√ß√µes s√£o blocos de c√≥digo reutiliz√°veis. Recebem par√¢metros e podem retornar um valor.</p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">saudacao</span>(<span class="variable">$nome</span>) {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">"Ol√°, $nome!"</span>;
    }

    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="function">saudacao</span>(<span class="string">"Maria"</span>);

    <span class="comment">// array_filter - filtra elementos</span>
    <span class="variable">$numeros</span> = [1,2,3,4,5];
    <span class="variable">$pares</span> = <span class="function">array_filter</span>(<span class="variable">$numeros</span>, <span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="variable">$n</span>) {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$n</span> % 2 == 0;
    });
    <span class="comment">// $pares = [2,4]</span>
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>

<h3 id="1.9">1.9 Lambda Functions (Fun√ß√µes An√¥nimas)</h3>
<p>S√£o fun√ß√µes sem nome, geralmente usadas como callback.</p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="variable">$saudacao</span> = <span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="variable">$nome</span>) {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">"Ol√°, $nome!"</span>;
    };
    <span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$saudacao</span>(<span class="string">"Jo√£o"</span>);

    <span class="comment">// Usando com array_map</span>
    <span class="variable">$dobro</span> = <span class="function">array_map</span>(<span class="keyword">function</span>(<span class="variable">$n</span>) {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$n</span> * 2;
    }, [1,2,3]);
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>

<h3 id="1.10">1.10 Separar L√≥gica do Template</h3>
<p>Um princ√≠pio importante: separe a l√≥gica PHP da apresenta√ß√£o (HTML). Crie um arquivo de l√≥gica e um template.</p>
<p><strong>index.php (l√≥gica):</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
    <span class="variable">$usuario</span> = <span class="string">'Jo√£o'</span>;
    <span class="variable">$posts</span> = [<span class="string">'Post 1'</span>, <span class="string">'Post 2'</span>];
    <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'views/index.view.php'</span>;
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>
<p><strong>views/index.view.php (template):</strong></p>
<pre><code>&lt;!DOCTYPE html&gt;
&lt;html&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
    &lt;title&gt;Meu Site&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;
&lt;body&gt;
    &lt;h1&gt;Ol√°, &lt;?= <span class="variable">$usuario</span> ?&gt;&lt;/h1&gt;
    &lt;ul&gt;
        &lt;?php <span class="keyword">foreach</span> (<span class="variable">$posts</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="variable">$post</span>) : ?&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;?= <span class="variable">$post</span> ?&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
        &lt;?php <span class="keyword">endforeach</span>; ?&gt;
    &lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</code></pre>

<h3 id="1.11">1.11 T√©cnicas de Refatora√ß√£o (B√°sico)</h3>
<p>Refatorar √© modificar o c√≥digo para torn√°-lo melhor sem alterar seu comportamento. Exemplo: extrair uma fun√ß√£o para reutilizar uma valida√ß√£o.</p>

<!-- ========== NOVA SE√á√ÉO COMPLETA: OPERADORES ========== -->
<h3 id="1.12">1.12 Operadores PHP (Tabela Completa)</h3>
<p>Operadores s√£o s√≠mbolos que realizam opera√ß√µes em vari√°veis e valores. Veja todos os tipos com exemplos pr√°ticos.</p>

<h4>1.12.1 Operadores Aritm√©ticos</h4>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>Operador</th><th>Nome</th><th>Exemplo</th><th>Resultado</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>+</code></td><td>Adi√ß√£o</td><td><code>5 + 3</code></td><td><code>8</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>-</code></td><td>Subtra√ß√£o</td><td><code>5 - 3</code></td><td><code>2</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>*</code></td><td>Multiplica√ß√£o</td><td><code>5 * 3</code></td><td><code>15</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>/</code></td><td>Divis√£o</td><td><code>5 / 2</code></td><td><code>2.5</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>%</code></td><td>M√≥dulo (resto)</td><td><code>5 % 2</code></td><td><code>1</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>**</code></td><td>Exponencia√ß√£o</td><td><code>5 ** 2</code></td><td><code>25</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h4>1.12.2 Operadores de Atribui√ß√£o</h4>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>Operador</th><th>Exemplo</th><th>Equivalente a</th><th>Descri√ß√£o</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>=</code></td><td><code>$x = 5</code></td><td>‚Äî</td><td>Atribui√ß√£o simples</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>+=</code></td><td><code>$x += 3</code></td><td><code>$x = $x + 3</code></td><td>Adi√ß√£o e atribui√ß√£o</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>-=</code></td><td><code>$x -= 3</code></td><td><code>$x = $x - 3</code></td><td>Subtra√ß√£o e atribui√ß√£o</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>*=</code></td><td><code>$x *= 3</code></td><td><code>$x = $x * 3</code></td><td>Multiplica√ß√£o e atribui√ß√£o</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>/=</code></td><td><code>$x /= 3</code></td><td><code>$x = $x / 3</code></td><td>Divis√£o e atribui√ß√£o</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>%=</code></td><td><code>$x %= 3</code></td><td><code>$x = $x % 3</code></td><td>M√≥dulo e atribui√ß√£o</td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>.=</code></td><td><code>$x .= "!"</code></td><td><code>$x = $x . "!"</code></td><td>Concatena√ß√£o e atribui√ß√£o</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h4>1.12.3 Operadores de Compara√ß√£o</h4>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>Operador</th><th>Nome</th><th>Exemplo</th><th>Resultado</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>==</code></td><td>Igual (valor)</td><td><code>5 == "5"</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>===</code></td><td>Id√™ntico (valor e tipo)</td><td><code>5 === "5"</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>!=</code> ou <code>&lt;&gt;</code></td><td>Diferente (valor)</td><td><code>5 != "5"</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>!==</code></td><td>N√£o id√™ntico</td><td><code>5 !== "5"</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>&lt;</code></td><td>Menor que</td><td><code>3 &lt; 5</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>&gt;</code></td><td>Maior que</td><td><code>3 &gt; 5</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>&lt;=</code></td><td>Menor ou igual</td><td><code>3 &lt;= 5</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>&gt;=</code></td><td>Maior ou igual</td><td><code>3 &gt;= 5</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>&lt;=&gt;</code></td><td>Spaceship (nave espacial)</td><td><code>1 &lt;=&gt; 2</code></td><td><code>-1</code> (0 igual, 1 maior)</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h4>1.12.4 Operadores L√≥gicos</h4>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>Operador</th><th>Nome</th><th>Exemplo</th><th>Resultado</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td><code>&amp;&amp;</code></td><td>E</td><td><code>true &amp;&amp; false</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>||</code></td><td>OU</td><td><code>true || false</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>!</code></td><td>N√ÉO</td><td><code>!true</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>and</code></td><td>E (baixa preced√™ncia)</td><td><code>true and false</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>or</code></td><td>OU (baixa preced√™ncia)</td><td><code>true or false</code></td><td><code>true</code></td></tr>
        <tr><td><code>xor</code></td><td>OU exclusivo</td><td><code>true xor true</code></td><td><code>false</code></td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h4>1.12.5 Operador de Concatena√ß√£o (.)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$nome</span> = <span class="string">"Jo√£o"</span>;
<span class="variable">$sobrenome</span> = <span class="string">"Silva"</span>;
<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$nome</span> . <span class="string">" "</span> . <span class="variable">$sobrenome</span>; <span class="comment">// Jo√£o Silva</span></code></pre>

<h4>1.12.6 Operador de Array (<code>=></code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$pessoa</span> = [
    <span class="string">'nome'</span> => <span class="string">'Maria'</span>,
    <span class="string">'idade'</span> => 30
];</code></pre>

<h4>1.12.7 Operador de Objeto (<code>-></code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$obj</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">stdClass</span>();
<span class="variable">$obj</span>-><span class="property">nome</span> = <span class="string">'Carlos'</span>;
<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$obj</span>-><span class="property">nome</span>; <span class="comment">// Carlos</span></code></pre>

<h4>1.12.8 Operador Tern√°rio (<code>?:</code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$idade</span> = 20;
<span class="variable">$status</span> = <span class="variable">$idade</span> >= 18 ? <span class="string">'Maior'</span> : <span class="string">'Menor'</span>;
<span class="comment">// $status = 'Maior'</span></code></pre>

<h4>1.12.9 Operador de Coalesc√™ncia Nula (<code>??</code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$nome</span> = <span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">'nome'</span>] ?? <span class="string">'Visitante'</span>;
<span class="comment">// Se $_GET['nome'] existir, usa ele; sen√£o, 'Visitante'</span></code></pre>

<h4>1.12.10 Operador de Coalesc√™ncia com Atribui√ß√£o (<code>??=</code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$carrinho</span> = null;
<span class="variable">$carrinho</span> ??= []; <span class="comment">// $carrinho = []</span>
<span class="variable">$carrinho</span> ??= [1,2,3]; <span class="comment">// continua []</span></code></pre>

<h4>1.12.11 Operador de Resolu√ß√£o de Escopo (<code>::</code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Database</span> {
    <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="constant">VERSION</span> = <span class="string">'1.0'</span>;
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="function">connect</span>() { }
}
<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="class">Database</span>::<span class="constant">VERSION</span>;
<span class="class">Database</span>::<span class="function">connect</span>();</code></pre>

<h4>1.12.12 Operador <code>instanceof</code></h4>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable">$db</span> <span class="keyword">instanceof</span> <span class="class">Database</span>) {
    <span class="comment">// √© uma inst√¢ncia de Database</span>
}</code></pre>

<h4>1.12.13 Operador de Supress√£o de Erro (<code>@</code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$conteudo</span> = @<span class="function">file_get_contents</span>(<span class="string">'nao-existe.txt'</span>);</code></pre>
<div class="note">
    <p><strong>Recomenda√ß√£o:</strong> Evite usar o operador <code>@</code>. Trate erros de forma adequada com exce√ß√µes ou verifica√ß√µes.</p>
</div>

<!-- ========== NOVA SE√á√ÉO COMPLETA: CLASSES E OBJETOS ========== -->
<h3 id="1.13">1.13 Introdu√ß√£o a Classes e Objetos</h3>
<p>Classes s√£o "moldes" para criar objetos. Elas encapsulam dados (propriedades) e comportamentos (m√©todos).</p>

<h4>1.13.1 Definindo uma Classe</h4>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Livro</span>
{
    <span class="comment">// Propriedades (atributos)</span>
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$titulo</span>;
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$autor</span>;
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$ano</span>;

    <span class="comment">// M√©todo (fun√ß√£o da classe)</span>
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">descricao</span>()
    {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="string">"{$this->titulo}, escrito por {$this->autor} em {$this->ano}."</span>;
    }
}
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>

<h4>1.13.2 Instanciando um Objeto</h4>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$livro1</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">Livro</span>();
<span class="variable">$livro1</span>-><span class="property">titulo</span> = <span class="string">'1984'</span>;
<span class="variable">$livro1</span>-><span class="property">autor</span> = <span class="string">'George Orwell'</span>;
<span class="variable">$livro1</span>-><span class="property">ano</span> = 1949;
<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$livro1</span>-><span class="function">descricao</span>();</code></pre>
<p><strong>Operador <code>-></code></strong>: acessa propriedades e m√©todos do objeto.</p>

<h4>1.13.3 M√©todo Construtor (<code>__construct</code>)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Usuario</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$nome</span>;
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$email</span>;

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">__construct</span>(<span class="variable">$nome</span>, <span class="variable">$email</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">nome</span> = <span class="variable">$nome</span>;
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">email</span> = <span class="variable">$email</span>;
    }
}

<span class="variable">$user</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">Usuario</span>(<span class="string">'Jo√£o'</span>, <span class="string">'joao@email.com'</span>);</code></pre>

<h4>1.13.4 Modificadores de Acesso (Visibilidade)</h4>
<ul>
    <li><code>public</code>: acess√≠vel de qualquer lugar.</li>
    <li><code>protected</code>: acess√≠vel na classe e em subclasses.</li>
    <li><code>private</code>: acess√≠vel apenas dentro da pr√≥pria classe.</li>
</ul>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">ContaBancaria</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">private</span> <span class="variable">$saldo</span> = 0;

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">depositar</span>(<span class="variable">$valor</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">saldo</span> += <span class="variable">$valor</span>;
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">getSaldo</span>()
    {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">saldo</span>;
    }
}</code></pre>

<h4>1.13.5 M√©todos Est√°ticos</h4>
<p>Pertencem √† classe, n√£o √† inst√¢ncia. Usam <code>::</code>.</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Matematica</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">somar</span>(<span class="variable">$a</span>, <span class="variable">$b</span>)
    {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$a</span> + <span class="variable">$b</span>;
    }
}

<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="class">Matematica</span>::<span class="function">somar</span>(5, 3); <span class="comment">// 8</span></code></pre>

<h4>1.13.6 Exemplo Pr√°tico: Classe Database (do curso)</h4>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Database</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$connection</span>;

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">__construct</span>(<span class="variable">$config</span>, <span class="variable">$username</span> = <span class="string">'root'</span>, <span class="variable">$password</span> = <span class="string">''</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$dsn</span> = <span class="string">'mysql:'</span> . <span class="function">http_build_query</span>(<span class="variable">$config</span>, <span class="string">''</span>, <span class="string">';'</span>);
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">connection</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">PDO</span>(<span class="variable">$dsn</span>, <span class="variable">$username</span>, <span class="variable">$password</span>, [
            <span class="class">PDO</span>::<span class="constant">ATTR_DEFAULT_FETCH_MODE</span> => <span class="class">PDO</span>::<span class="constant">FETCH_ASSOC</span>
        ]);
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">query</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>, <span class="variable">$params</span> = [])
    {
        <span class="variable">$statement</span> = <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">connection</span>-><span class="function">prepare</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>);
        <span class="variable">$statement</span>-><span class="function">execute</span>(<span class="variable">$params</span>);
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$statement</span>;
    }
}</code></pre>

<hr id="s2">

<!-- ========== SE√á√ÉO 2 ‚Äì APLICA√á√ïES WEB DIN√ÇMICAS ========== -->
<h1>2. APLICA√á√ïES WEB DIN√ÇMICAS</h1>

<h3 id="2.1">2.1 Page Links (Links entre P√°ginas)</h3>
<p>Para navega√ß√£o, usamos links HTML. Par√¢metros na URL s√£o capturados via <code>$_GET</code>.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;a href="about.php"&gt;Sobre&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;a href="note.php?id=1"&gt;Nota 1&lt;/a&gt;

<span class="comment">&lt;!-- Em note.php --&gt;</span>
<span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span> <span class="variable">$id</span> = <span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>]; <span class="comment">// 1</span> <span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>

<h3 id="2.2">2.2 PHP Partials</h3>
<p>Reutilize partes do HTML (header, nav, footer) com <code>require</code> ou <code>include</code>.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;?php <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'partials/header.php'</span>; ?&gt;
&lt;?php <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'partials/nav.php'</span>; ?&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Conte√∫do da p√°gina&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;?php <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'partials/footer.php'</span>; ?&gt;</code></pre>

<h3 id="2.3">2.3 Superglobais e Estiliza√ß√£o por P√°gina</h3>
<p><code>$_SERVER['REQUEST_URI']</code> cont√©m a URL atual. Use para destacar o link ativo.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;?php <span class="variable">$uri</span> = <span class="variable">$_SERVER</span>[<span class="string">'REQUEST_URI'</span>]; ?&gt;
&lt;nav&gt;
    &lt;a href="/" class="&lt;?= <span class="variable">$uri</span> === <span class="string">'/'</span> ? <span class="string">'active'</span> : <span class="string">''</span> ?&gt;"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;
    &lt;a href="/about" class="&lt;?= <span class="variable">$uri</span> === <span class="string">'/about'</span> ? <span class="string">'active'</span> : <span class="string">''</span> ?&gt;"&gt;Sobre&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/nav&gt;</code></pre>

<h3 id="2.4">2.4 Criar um Roteador (Router) do Zero</h3>
<p>Um roteador mapeia URLs para controladores. Arquivo <code>index.php</code> como front controller.</p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// index.php</span>
<span class="variable">$uri</span> = <span class="function">parse_url</span>(<span class="variable">$_SERVER</span>[<span class="string">'REQUEST_URI'</span>], <span class="class">PHP_URL_PATH</span>);
<span class="variable">$routes</span> = <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'routes.php'</span>;

<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">routeToController</span>(<span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$routes</span>) {
    <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="function">array_key_exists</span>(<span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$routes</span>)) {
        <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="variable">$routes</span>[<span class="variable">$uri</span>];
    } <span class="keyword">else</span> {
        <span class="function">abort</span>(404);
    }
}

<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">abort</span>(<span class="variable">$code</span>) {
    <span class="function">http_response_code</span>(<span class="variable">$code</span>);
    <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">"views/{$code}.php"</span>;
    <span class="keyword">die</span>();
}

<span class="function">routeToController</span>(<span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$routes</span>);</code></pre>

<p><strong>routes.php</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="keyword">return</span> [
    <span class="string">'/'</span> => <span class="string">'controllers/index.php'</span>,
    <span class="string">'/about'</span> => <span class="string">'controllers/about.php'</span>,
    <span class="string">'/contact'</span> => <span class="string">'controllers/contact.php'</span>
];
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span></code></pre>

<h3 id="2.5">2.5 Criar um Banco de Dados MySQL</h3>
<p>Use SQL para criar o banco e as tabelas.</p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">-- Via terminal ou phpMyAdmin</span>
CREATE DATABASE meusite;
USE meusite;

CREATE TABLE posts (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    titulo VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    conteudo TEXT,
    data_criacao TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);</code></pre>

<h3 id="2.6">2.6 Primeiros Passos com PDO</h3>
<p>PDO (PHP Data Objects) √© a extens√£o segura para acessar bancos de dados.</p>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$dsn</span> = <span class="string">"mysql:host=localhost;port=3306;dbname=meusite;charset=utf8mb4"</span>;
<span class="variable">$usuario</span> = <span class="string">'root'</span>;
<span class="variable">$senha</span> = <span class="string">''</span>;

<span class="keyword">try</span> {
    <span class="variable">$pdo</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">PDO</span>(<span class="variable">$dsn</span>, <span class="variable">$usuario</span>, <span class="variable">$senha</span>);
    <span class="variable">$pdo</span>-><span class="function">setAttribute</span>(<span class="class">PDO</span>::<span class="constant">ATTR_ERRMODE</span>, <span class="class">PDO</span>::<span class="constant">ERRMODE_EXCEPTION</span>);
} <span class="keyword">catch</span> (<span class="class">PDOException</span> <span class="variable">$e</span>) {
    <span class="keyword">die</span>(<span class="string">"Falha na conex√£o: "</span> . <span class="variable">$e</span>-><span class="function">getMessage</span>());
}

<span class="variable">$query</span> = <span class="string">"SELECT * FROM posts"</span>;
<span class="variable">$statement</span> = <span class="variable">$pdo</span>-><span class="function">query</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>);
<span class="variable">$posts</span> = <span class="variable">$statement</span>-><span class="function">fetchAll</span>(<span class="class">PDO</span>::<span class="constant">FETCH_ASSOC</span>);</code></pre>

<h3 id="2.7">2.7 Extrair uma Classe Database</h3>
<p>Criamos uma classe para centralizar a conex√£o e consultas.</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Database</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="variable">$connection</span>;

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">__construct</span>(<span class="variable">$config</span>, <span class="variable">$username</span> = <span class="string">'root'</span>, <span class="variable">$password</span> = <span class="string">''</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$dsn</span> = <span class="string">'mysql:'</span> . <span class="function">http_build_query</span>(<span class="variable">$config</span>, <span class="string">''</span>, <span class="string">';'</span>);
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">connection</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">PDO</span>(<span class="variable">$dsn</span>, <span class="variable">$username</span>, <span class="variable">$password</span>, [
            <span class="class">PDO</span>::<span class="constant">ATTR_DEFAULT_FETCH_MODE</span> => <span class="class">PDO</span>::<span class="constant">FETCH_ASSOC</span>
        ]);
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">query</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>, <span class="variable">$params</span> = [])
    {
        <span class="variable">$statement</span> = <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">connection</span>-><span class="function">prepare</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>);
        <span class="variable">$statement</span>-><span class="function">execute</span>(<span class="variable">$params</span>);
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$statement</span>;
    }
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="2.8">2.8 Configura√ß√£o e Flexibilidade de Ambientes</h3>
<p>Separe as configura√ß√µes em um arquivo e carregue conforme o ambiente.</p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// config.php</span>
<span class="php-tag">&lt;?php</span>
<span class="keyword">return</span> [
    <span class="string">'database'</span> => [
        <span class="string">'host'</span> => <span class="string">'localhost'</span>,
        <span class="string">'port'</span> => 3306,
        <span class="string">'dbname'</span> => <span class="string">'meusite'</span>,
        <span class="string">'charset'</span> => <span class="string">'utf8mb4'</span>
    ]
];
<span class="php-tag">?&gt;</span>

<span class="comment">// index.php</span>
<span class="variable">$config</span> = <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'config.php'</span>;
<span class="variable">$db</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">Database</span>(<span class="variable">$config</span>[<span class="string">'database'</span>]);</code></pre>

<h3 id="2.9">2.9 SQL Injection e Prepared Statements</h3>
<p><strong>Nunca</strong> concatene valores diretamente na SQL. Use prepared statements.</p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// ERRADO!</span>
<span class="variable">$id</span> = <span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>];
<span class="variable">$query</span> = <span class="string">"SELECT * FROM posts WHERE id = $id"</span>;

<span class="comment">// CORRETO</span>
<span class="variable">$query</span> = <span class="string">"SELECT * FROM posts WHERE id = :id"</span>;
<span class="variable">$statement</span> = <span class="variable">$db</span>-><span class="property">connection</span>-><span class="function">prepare</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>);
<span class="variable">$statement</span>-><span class="function">execute</span>([<span class="string">'id'</span> => <span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>]]);
<span class="variable">$post</span> = <span class="variable">$statement</span>-><span class="function">fetch</span>();</code></pre>

<hr id="s3">

<!-- ========== SE√á√ÉO 3 ‚Äì NOTES MINI-PROJECT ========== -->
<h1>3. MINI-PROJETO: APLICATIVO DE NOTAS</h1>

<h3 id="3.1">3.1 Tabelas e √çndices no Banco</h3>
<pre><code>CREATE TABLE users (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    nome VARCHAR(255),
    email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
    senha VARCHAR(255)
);

CREATE TABLE notes (
    id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    body TEXT,
    user_id INT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    INDEX(user_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (user_id) REFERENCES users(id)
);</code></pre>

<h3 id="3.2">3.2 Renderizar Notas e P√°gina de Nota Individual</h3>
<p><strong>Controlador para listar notas:</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// controllers/notes.php</span>
<span class="variable">$db</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">Database</span>(<span class="variable">$config</span>[<span class="string">'database'</span>]);
<span class="variable">$query</span> = <span class="string">"SELECT * FROM notes WHERE user_id = 1"</span>;
<span class="variable">$notes</span> = <span class="variable">$db</span>-><span class="function">query</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>)-><span class="function">fetchAll</span>();
<span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'views/notes/index.view.php'</span>;</code></pre>

<p><strong>View index.view.php:</strong></p>
<pre><code>&lt;ul&gt;
    &lt;?php <span class="keyword">foreach</span> (<span class="variable">$notes</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="variable">$note</span>) : ?&gt;
        &lt;li&gt;
            &lt;a href="/note?id=&lt;?= <span class="variable">$note</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>] ?&gt;"&gt;
                &lt;?= <span class="function">htmlspecialchars</span>(<span class="variable">$note</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>]) ?&gt;
            &lt;/a&gt;
        &lt;/li&gt;
    &lt;?php <span class="keyword">endforeach</span>; ?&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</code></pre>

<p><strong>Controlador de nota √∫nica:</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// controllers/note.php</span>
<span class="variable">$db</span> = <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">Database</span>(<span class="variable">$config</span>[<span class="string">'database'</span>]);
<span class="variable">$query</span> = <span class="string">"SELECT * FROM notes WHERE id = :id"</span>;
<span class="variable">$note</span> = <span class="variable">$db</span>-><span class="function">query</span>(<span class="variable">$query</span>, [<span class="string">'id'</span> => <span class="variable">$_GET</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>]])-><span class="function">fetch</span>();

<span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="variable">$note</span>) {
    <span class="function">abort</span>(404);
}

<span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'views/notes/show.view.php'</span>;</code></pre>

<h3 id="3.3">3.3 Introdu√ß√£o √† Autoriza√ß√£o</h3>
<p>Verificar se o usu√°rio logado √© o dono da nota.</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable">$note</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>] !== <span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>]) {
    <span class="function">abort</span>(403); <span class="comment">// Proibido</span>
}</code></pre>

<p><strong>Constantes para c√≥digos HTTP:</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Response</span> {
    <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="constant">NOT_FOUND</span> = 404;
    <span class="keyword">const</span> <span class="constant">FORBIDDEN</span> = 403;
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="3.4">3.4 Programa√ß√£o √© Reescrita (Refatora√ß√£o)</h3>
<p>Extraia a l√≥gica de autoriza√ß√£o para uma fun√ß√£o.</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">authorize</span>(<span class="variable">$condition</span>, <span class="variable">$status</span> = <span class="class">Response</span>::<span class="constant">FORBIDDEN</span>) {
    <span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="variable">$condition</span>) {
        <span class="function">abort</span>(<span class="variable">$status</span>);
    }
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="3.5">3.5 Introdu√ß√£o a Formul√°rios e M√©todos de Requisi√ß√£o</h3>
<p>Formul√°rio para criar nota (POST).</p>
<pre><code>&lt;form method="POST" action="/notes"&gt;
    &lt;textarea name="body"&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
    &lt;button type="submit"&gt;Criar&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>

<p>No controlador:</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable">$_SERVER</span>[<span class="string">'REQUEST_METHOD'</span>] === <span class="string">'POST'</span>) {
    <span class="variable">$db</span>-><span class="function">query</span>(<span class="string">"INSERT INTO notes (body, user_id) VALUES (:body, :user_id)"</span>, [
        <span class="string">'body'</span> => <span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>],
        <span class="string">'user_id'</span> => 1
    ]);
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="3.6">3.6 Sempre Escape Dados N√£o Confi√°veis (XSS)</h3>
<p>Ao exibir dados vindos do usu√°rio, use <code>htmlspecialchars()</code>.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;?= <span class="function">htmlspecialchars</span>(<span class="variable">$note</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>]) ?&gt;</code></pre>

<h3 id="3.7">3.7 Introdu√ß√£o √† Valida√ß√£o de Formul√°rios</h3>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$errors</span> = [];

<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="function">strlen</span>(<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>]) === 0) {
    <span class="variable">$errors</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>] = <span class="string">'O corpo da nota √© obrigat√≥rio.'</span>;
}

<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="function">strlen</span>(<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>]) > 1000) {
    <span class="variable">$errors</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>] = <span class="string">'A nota deve ter no m√°ximo 1000 caracteres.'</span>;
}

<span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="function">empty</span>(<span class="variable">$errors</span>)) {
    <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'views/notes/create.view.php'</span>;
    <span class="keyword">die</span>();
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="3.8">3.8 Extrair uma Classe Validator</h3>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Validator</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">string</span>(<span class="variable">$value</span>, <span class="variable">$min</span> = 1, <span class="variable">$max</span> = INF)
    {
        <span class="variable">$value</span> = <span class="function">trim</span>(<span class="variable">$value</span>);
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="function">strlen</span>(<span class="variable">$value</span>) >= <span class="variable">$min</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="function">strlen</span>(<span class="variable">$value</span>) <= <span class="variable">$max</span>;
    }
}

<span class="comment">// Uso</span>
<span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="class">Validator</span>::<span class="function">string</span>(<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>], 1, 1000)) {
    <span class="variable">$errors</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>] = <span class="string">'A nota deve ter entre 1 e 1000 caracteres.'</span>;
}</code></pre>

<hr id="s4">

<!-- ========== SE√á√ÉO 4 ‚Äì ORGANIZA√á√ÉO DO PROJETO ========== -->
<h1>4. ORGANIZA√á√ÉO DO PROJETO</h1>

<h3 id="4.1">4.1 Conven√ß√µes de Nomenclatura para Recursos</h3>
<p>Seguir um padr√£o RESTful ajuda na organiza√ß√£o.</p>
<table>
    <thead><tr><th>A√ß√£o</th><th>Rota</th><th>M√©todo</th><th>Controller/M√©todo</th></tr></thead>
    <tbody>
        <tr><td>Listar</td><td>/notes</td><td>GET</td><td>index()</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Exibir uma</td><td>/note?id=1</td><td>GET</td><td>show()</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Exibir form cria√ß√£o</td><td>/notes/create</td><td>GET</td><td>create()</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Armazenar</td><td>/notes</td><td>POST</td><td>store()</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Exibir form edi√ß√£o</td><td>/note/edit?id=1</td><td>GET</td><td>edit()</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Atualizar</td><td>/note</td><td>PATCH</td><td>update()</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Deletar</td><td>/note</td><td>DELETE</td><td>destroy()</td></tr>
    </tbody>
</table>

<h3 id="4.2">4.2 Autoloading e Extra√ß√£o de Fun√ß√µes</h3>
<pre><code><span class="function">spl_autoload_register</span>(<span class="keyword">function</span> (<span class="variable">$class</span>) {
    <span class="variable">$class</span> = <span class="function">str_replace</span>(<span class="string">'\\'</span>, <span class="class">DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR</span>, <span class="variable">$class</span>);
    <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="function">base_path</span>(<span class="string">"{$class}.php"</span>);
});

<span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">base_path</span>(<span class="variable">$path</span>)
{
    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="class">__DIR__</span> . <span class="string">'/'</span> . <span class="variable">$path</span>;
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="4.3">4.3 Namespaces</h3>
<p>Organizam classes em pastas virtuais.</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">namespace</span> <span class="class">Core</span>;

<span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Database</span> { }

<span class="comment">// Em outro arquivo</span>
<span class="keyword">use</span> <span class="class">Core</span>\<span class="class">Database</span>;</code></pre>

<h3 id="4.4">4.4 Lidar com M√∫ltiplos M√©todos de Requisi√ß√£o no Controller</h3>
<p>Em vez de um √∫nico controller com switch, separe em arquivos ou m√©todos distintos.</p>

<h3 id="4.5">4.5 Construir um Roteador Melhor</h3>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Router</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">protected</span> <span class="variable">$routes</span> = [];

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">add</span>(<span class="variable">$method</span>, <span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$controller</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">routes</span>[] = [
            <span class="string">'uri'</span> => <span class="variable">$uri</span>,
            <span class="string">'controller'</span> => <span class="variable">$controller</span>,
            <span class="string">'method'</span> => <span class="variable">$method</span>
        ];
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">get</span>(<span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$controller</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="function">add</span>(<span class="string">'GET'</span>, <span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$controller</span>);
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">post</span>(<span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$controller</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="function">add</span>(<span class="string">'POST'</span>, <span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$controller</span>);
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">route</span>(<span class="variable">$uri</span>, <span class="variable">$method</span>)
    {
        <span class="keyword">foreach</span> (<span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">routes</span> <span class="keyword">as</span> <span class="variable">$route</span>) {
            <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable">$route</span>[<span class="string">'uri'</span>] === <span class="variable">$uri</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="variable">$route</span>[<span class="string">'method'</span>] === <span class="function">strtoupper</span>(<span class="variable">$method</span>)) {
                <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="function">base_path</span>(<span class="variable">$route</span>[<span class="string">'controller'</span>]);
            }
        }
        <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="function">abort</span>();
    }
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="4.6">4.6 Uma Requisi√ß√£o, Um Controlador</h3>
<p>Cada controlador deve ser respons√°vel por uma √∫nica a√ß√£o (ex: <code>NotesStoreController</code>).</p>

<h3 id="4.7">4.7 Seu Primeiro Container de Servi√ßos</h3>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">App</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">protected</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="variable">$container</span> = [];

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">bind</span>(<span class="variable">$key</span>, <span class="variable">$resolver</span>)
    {
        <span class="keyword">static</span>::<span class="variable">$container</span>[<span class="variable">$key</span>] = <span class="variable">$resolver</span>;
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">static</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">resolve</span>(<span class="variable">$key</span>)
    {
        <span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="function">array_key_exists</span>(<span class="variable">$key</span>, <span class="keyword">static</span>::<span class="variable">$container</span>)) {
            <span class="keyword">throw</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">Exception</span>(<span class="string">"No binding for {$key}"</span>);
        }
        <span class="variable">$resolver</span> = <span class="keyword">static</span>::<span class="variable">$container</span>[<span class="variable">$key</span>];
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="function">call_user_func</span>(<span class="variable">$resolver</span>);
    }
}</code></pre>

<p><strong>Registrando depend√™ncias:</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="class">App</span>::<span class="function">bind</span>(<span class="string">'config'</span>, <span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'config.php'</span>);
<span class="class">App</span>::<span class="function">bind</span>(<span class="string">'database'</span>, <span class="keyword">function</span>() {
    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">new</span> <span class="class">Database</span>(<span class="class">App</span>::<span class="function">resolve</span>(<span class="string">'config'</span>)[<span class="string">'database'</span>]);
});</code></pre>

<h3 id="4.8">4.8 Atualizando com Requisi√ß√µes PATCH</h3>
<p>Formul√°rio HTML n√£o suporta PATCH nativamente; usamos um campo escondido <code>_method</code>.</p>
<pre><code>&lt;form method="POST" action="/note"&gt;
    &lt;input type="hidden" name="_method" value="PATCH"&gt;
    &lt;input type="hidden" name="id" value="&lt;?= <span class="variable">$note</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>] ?&gt;"&gt;
    &lt;textarea name="body"&gt;&lt;?= <span class="function">htmlspecialchars</span>(<span class="variable">$note</span>[<span class="string">'body'</span>]) ?&gt;&lt;/textarea&gt;
    &lt;button&gt;Atualizar&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;/form&gt;</code></pre>

<p>No roteador, verifique <code>$_POST['_method']</code> e sobrescreva o m√©todo.</p>

<hr id="s5">

<!-- ========== SE√á√ÉO 5 ‚Äì SESS√ïES E AUTENTICA√á√ÉO ========== -->
<h1>5. SESS√ïES E AUTENTICA√á√ÉO</h1>

<h3 id="5.1">5.1 Sess√µes PHP 101</h3>
<pre><code><span class="function">session_start</span>(); <span class="comment">// deve ser chamado antes de qualquer sa√≠da</span>
<span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>] = 1;
<span class="keyword">echo</span> <span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>];</code></pre>

<h3 id="5.2">5.2 Registrar um Novo Usu√°rio</h3>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// Valida√ß√µes...</span>
<span class="variable">$db</span>-><span class="function">query</span>(<span class="string">"INSERT INTO users (email, senha, nome) VALUES (:email, :senha, :nome)"</span>, [
    <span class="string">'email'</span> => <span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'email'</span>],
    <span class="string">'senha'</span> => <span class="function">password_hash</span>(<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'senha'</span>], <span class="class">PASSWORD_BCRYPT</span>),
    <span class="string">'nome'</span> => <span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'nome'</span>]
]);

<span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>] = <span class="variable">$db</span>-><span class="property">connection</span>-><span class="function">lastInsertId</span>();</code></pre>

<h3 id="5.3">5.3 Introdu√ß√£o ao Middleware</h3>
<p>Classe que verifica autentica√ß√£o antes de acessar a rota.</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">AuthMiddleware</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">handle</span>()
    {
        <span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="function">isset</span>(<span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>])) {
            <span class="function">header</span>(<span class="string">'Location: /login'</span>);
            <span class="keyword">exit</span>();
        }
    }
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="5.4">5.4 Gerencie Senhas com Bcrypt (password_hash)</h3>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// Hash da senha</span>
<span class="variable">$hash</span> = <span class="function">password_hash</span>(<span class="string">'minha_senha'</span>, <span class="class">PASSWORD_BCRYPT</span>);

<span class="comment">// Verifica√ß√£o</span>
<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="function">password_verify</span>(<span class="variable">$senhaDigitada</span>, <span class="variable">$hashArmazenado</span>)) {
    <span class="comment">// senha correta</span>
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="5.5">5.5 Login e Logout</h3>
<p><strong>Login:</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="variable">$user</span> = <span class="variable">$db</span>-><span class="function">query</span>(<span class="string">"SELECT * FROM users WHERE email = :email"</span>, [
    <span class="string">'email'</span> => <span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'email'</span>]
])-><span class="function">fetch</span>();

<span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable">$user</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="function">password_verify</span>(<span class="variable">$_POST</span>[<span class="string">'senha'</span>], <span class="variable">$user</span>[<span class="string">'senha'</span>])) {
    <span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>] = <span class="variable">$user</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>];
    <span class="function">header</span>(<span class="string">'Location: /'</span>);
    <span class="keyword">exit</span>();
}</code></pre>

<p><strong>Logout:</strong></p>
<pre><code><span class="function">session_start</span>();
<span class="function">session_destroy</span>();
<span class="function">header</span>(<span class="string">'Location: /'</span>);
<span class="keyword">exit</span>();</code></pre>

<hr id="s6">

<!-- ========== SE√á√ÉO 6 ‚Äì REFATORA√á√ÉO AVAN√áADA ========== -->
<h1>6. T√âCNICAS DE REFATORA√á√ÉO</h1>

<h3 id="6.1">6.1 Extrair um Objeto de Valida√ß√£o de Formul√°rio</h3>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">LoginForm</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">protected</span> <span class="variable">$errors</span> = [];

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">validate</span>(<span class="variable">$email</span>, <span class="variable">$password</span>)
    {
        <span class="keyword">if</span> (! <span class="class">Validator</span>::<span class="function">email</span>(<span class="variable">$email</span>)) {
            <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">errors</span>[<span class="string">'email'</span>] = <span class="string">'E-mail inv√°lido.'</span>;
        }
        <span class="comment">// ... mais valida√ß√µes</span>
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="function">empty</span>(<span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">errors</span>);
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">errors</span>()
    {
        <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="property">errors</span>;
    }
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="6.2">6.2 Extrair uma Classe Authenticator</h3>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="class">Authenticator</span>
{
    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">attempt</span>(<span class="variable">$email</span>, <span class="variable">$password</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$user</span> = <span class="class">App</span>::<span class="function">resolve</span>(<span class="string">'database'</span>)-><span class="function">query</span>(<span class="string">"SELECT * FROM users WHERE email = :email"</span>, [
            <span class="string">'email'</span> => <span class="variable">$email</span>
        ])-><span class="function">fetch</span>();

        <span class="keyword">if</span> (<span class="variable">$user</span> &amp;&amp; <span class="function">password_verify</span>(<span class="variable">$password</span>, <span class="variable">$user</span>[<span class="string">'senha'</span>])) {
            <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="function">login</span>(<span class="variable">$user</span>);
            <span class="keyword">return</span> true;
        }
        <span class="keyword">return</span> false;
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">login</span>(<span class="variable">$user</span>)
    {
        <span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'user_id'</span>] = <span class="variable">$user</span>[<span class="string">'id'</span>];
    }

    <span class="keyword">public</span> <span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">logout</span>()
    {
        <span class="function">session_destroy</span>();
    }
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="6.3">6.3 Padr√£o PRG (Post-Redirect-Get) e Session Flashing</h3>
<p>Ap√≥s um POST, redirecione para evitar reenvio do formul√°rio. Use flash data para erros e dados antigos.</p>
<pre><code><span class="comment">// No controller, em caso de erro</span>
<span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'_flash'</span>][<span class="string">'errors'</span>] = <span class="variable">$form</span>-><span class="function">errors</span>();
<span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'_flash'</span>][<span class="string">'old'</span>] = <span class="variable">$_POST</span>;
<span class="function">header</span>(<span class="string">'Location: /login'</span>);
<span class="keyword">exit</span>();</code></pre>

<h3 id="6.4">6.4 Flash Old Form Data</h3>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">function</span> <span class="function">old</span>(<span class="variable">$key</span>, <span class="variable">$default</span> = <span class="string">''</span>)
{
    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="variable">$_SESSION</span>[<span class="string">'_flash'</span>][<span class="string">'old'</span>][<span class="variable">$key</span>] ?? <span class="variable">$default</span>;
}</code></pre>

<h3 id="6.5">6.5 Redirecionamento Autom√°tico ao Falhar Valida√ß√£o</h3>
<p>Pode ser implementado com exce√ß√µes ou m√©todos de retorno na pr√≥pria classe de formul√°rio.</p>

