<!-- ========== SE√á√ÉO 7 ‚Äì COMPOSER ========== -->
<h1>7. COMPOSER</h1>

<h3 id="7.1">7.1 Composer e Autoloading Gratuito</h3>
<p>Composer √© o gerenciador de depend√™ncias do PHP. Crie um <code>composer.json</code>:</p>
<pre><code>{
    "autoload": {
        "classmap": [
            "app"
        ],
        "psr-4": {
            "Core\\": "Core/",
            "App\\": "App/"
        }
    }
}</code></pre>
<p>Execute <code>composer dump-autoload</code> e inclua:</p>
<pre><code><span class="keyword">require</span> <span class="string">'vendor/autoload.php'</span>;</code></pre>

<h3 id="7.2">7.2 Instalar Pacotes: Collections e PestPHP</h3>
<pre><code>composer require illuminate/collections
composer require pestphp/pest --dev</code></pre>

