<!-- ========== SE√á√ÉO 8 ‚Äì TESTES ========== -->
<h1>8. TESTES</h1>

<h3 id="8.1">8.1 Abordagens, Termos e Considera√ß√µes</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Unit√°rios:</strong> testam uma unidade isolada (classe/m√©todo).</li>
    <li><strong>Feature:</strong> testam um recurso completo (rota, controlador).</li>
    <li><strong>Aceita√ß√£o:</strong> simulam o navegador.</li>
</ul>
<p>Exemplo com Pest:</p>
<pre><code><span class="function">test</span>(<span class="string">'usu√°rio pode se registrar'</span>, <span class="keyword">function</span>() {
    <span class="variable">$response</span> = <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="function">post</span>(<span class="string">'/register'</span>, [
        <span class="string">'email'</span> => <span class="string">'teste@exemplo.com'</span>,
        <span class="string">'password'</span> => <span class="string">'secret'</span>
    ]);
    <span class="variable">$response</span>-><span class="function">assertRedirect</span>(<span class="string">'/'</span>);
    <span class="variable">$this</span>-><span class="function">assertDatabaseHas</span>(<span class="string">'users'</span>, [<span class="string">'email'</span> => <span class="string">'teste@exemplo.com'</span>]);
});</code></pre>

